data.description: This custom, single-level home in Hassayampa Village exudes tranquility. The gourmet kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, smooth alder cabinets, paired with granite counters, creating a beautiful culinary space. Throughout, the elegance of wood floors is showcased. The great-room, adorned with bookshelves, seamlessly connects with nature through French doors leading to one of three covered patios. The main bedroom offers ample space, while it's bath indulges with a jetted tub and a heated towel bar. The intelligently designed split floor plan includes a Jack & Jill bath for guest privacy, along with a separate patio. All of this is embraced by the serenity of a seasonal creek, completing this truly peaceful retreat.
